reviewText: Bought this for my husband (the man who has everything) for Christmas.  The family watched the first two cd's together on Christmas Eve and laughed till we cried.  It was nice to share a piece of TV history with the younger generation.  This can be watched over and over without tiring of the humor.  Thanks for the great value.

well me and my brother got the disk for our mom for christmas and she loved them. didn't realy watch most of the shows. but she said they were good. but as long as she was happy that is what counts the most.
